{"customEmbed": {"name": "MI CLEAN HTML 3", "enabled": true, "loadOnce": false, "position": "BODY_END", "embedData": {"category": "ESSENTIAL", "html": "<section class=\"sec\" id=\"camasirxana\">\n  <div class=\"sec-top rv\">\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:14px\"><span class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"display:inline-flex;margin:0\">02 / Cama\u015f\u0131rxana</span> <span class=\"tag\">58 M\u0259hsul \u00b7 9 Alt Kateqoriya</span></div>\n      <h2 class=\"h2\">Cama\u015f\u0131rxana <b>M\u0259hsullar\u0131</b></h2>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"sec-desc\">S\u0259naye yuyucu, yum\u015fald\u0131c\u0131, a\u011fartma, dozaj sisteml\u0259ri. Enerji q\u0259na\u0259tli low-temp formulalar. 5 ulduzlu tekstil keyfiyy\u0259ti \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pg pg3 rv\">\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582735689369-4fe89db7114c?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"S\u0259naye cama\u015f\u0131rxanas\u0131 \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn yuyucu toz deterjan\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-code\">CAM-001 / Toz</div><div class=\"pc-name\">S\u0259naye Yuyucu Toz \u2014 Y\u00fcks\u0259k Aktivlik</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Surfactants + sodium carbonate + enzymes</li><li>G\u00fccl\u00fc t\u0259sirli \u2014 40\u00b0C \u2013 95\u00b0C</li><li>\u00c7ar\u015faf \u00b7 D\u0259smal \u00b7 Uniforma</li><li>\u018ftirsiz &amp; eco variantlar var</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 10 / 25 kg</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1626806819282-2c1dc01a5e0c?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"S\u0259naye maye cama\u015f\u0131r deterjan\u0131 \u015f\u00fc\u015f\u0259si\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-code\">CAM-002 / Maye</div><div class=\"pc-name\">S\u0259naye Yuyucu Maye \u2014 Low-Temp</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Surfactants + enzymes \u2014 dose pump</li><li>30\u00b0C \u2013 60\u00b0C a\u015fa\u011f\u0131 temperatur</li><li>Enerji q\u0259na\u0259ti \u2014 avtomatik dozaj</li><li>\u018ftirsiz &amp; eco variantlar var</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 5 / 20 L</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1545173168-9f1947eebb7f?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Yum\u015faq a\u011f otel d\u0259smallar\u0131 \u2014 tekstil toxumas\u0131\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-code\">CAM-003 / Yum\u015fald\u0131c\u0131</div><div class=\"pc-name\">Tekstil Yum\u015fald\u0131c\u0131 Konsentrat</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Cationic surfactants \u2014 industrial grade</li><li>Yum\u015faql\u0131q + anti-static effekt</li><li>L\u00fcks otel toxumalar\u0131 \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 5 / 20 L</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"tbl-w rv\" style=\"margin-top:36px\">\n    <table class=\"tbl\">\n      <thead><tr><th>M\u0259hsul</th><th>Formulasiya</th><th>Texniki</th><th>H\u0259cm</th></tr></thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Oksigen bleach (powder)</td><td class=\"tm\">Sodium percarbonate</td><td class=\"tm\">Xlorsuz a\u011fartma</td><td class=\"tm\">5 / 10 kg</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">pH Neutralizer (sour)</td><td class=\"tm\">Citric/lactic acid</td><td class=\"tm\">Son yaxalama \u0259lav\u0259si</td><td class=\"tm\">5 / 20 L</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Tekstil ni\u015fastas\u0131 (starch)</td><td class=\"tm\">Modified starch</td><td class=\"tm\">\u00dct\u00fcl\u0259m\u0259 d\u0259st\u0259yi</td><td class=\"tm\">5 / 20 L</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Anti-foam (defoamer)</td><td class=\"tm\">Silicone-based antifoam</td><td class=\"tm\">A\u015fa\u011f\u0131 dozaj</td><td class=\"tm\">1 / 5 L</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Cama\u015f\u0131rxana dezinfektant \u0259lav\u0259si</td><td class=\"tm\">Hydrogen peroxide or QAC</td><td class=\"tm\">A\u015fa\u011f\u0131 temperatur dezinfeksiyas\u0131</td><td class=\"tm\">5 / 20 L</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"sub rv\">Dozaj Sisteml\u0259ri <big>Avadanl\u0131q &amp; Pompalar</big></div>\n  <div class=\"pg rv\">\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1635070041078-e363dbe005cb?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"S\u0259naye kimy\u0259vi dozaj pompas\u0131 \u2014 venturi sistemi\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">6 \u00c7\u0131x\u0131\u015fl\u0131 Venturi Pompas\u0131</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Kimy\u0259vi avtomatik dozaj</li><li>Venturi sistemi</li></ul></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581244277943-fe4a9c777189?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Peristalgik pompa \u2014 d\u0259qiq kimy\u0259vi dozaj\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">6 \u00c7\u0131x\u0131\u015fl\u0131 Peristalgik Pompa</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Daha d\u0259qiq dozaj</li><li>Programmla\u015fd\u0131r\u0131la bil\u0259n</li></ul></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504328345606-18bbc8c9d7d1?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"\u00c7oxfunksiyal\u0131 kimy\u0259vi qar\u0131\u015fd\u0131r\u0131c\u0131 avadanl\u0131q\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">4 / 8 Pozisiyal\u0131 Qar\u0131\u015fd\u0131r\u0131c\u0131</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>\u00c7ox m\u0259hsullu seyr\u0259ltm\u0259</li><li>4 v\u0259 8 pozisiya</li></ul></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563453392212-326f5e854473?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Mobil k\u00f6p\u00fckl\u0259m\u0259 aparat\u0131 \u2014 s\u0259naye t\u0259mizliyi\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">Mobil K\u00f6p\u00fck Aparat\u0131</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Da\u015f\u0131nan k\u00f6p\u00fckl\u0259m\u0259 qur\u011fusu</li><li>M\u0259tb\u0259x &amp; cama\u015f\u0131rxana</li></ul></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Kommersiya qabyuyan ma\u015f\u0131n dozaj pompas\u0131\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">Qabyuyan Ma\u015f\u0131n Pompas\u0131</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Vaxt idar\u0259li ikili pompa</li><li>Rinse aid + deterjan</li></ul></div></div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- M\u018fTB\u018fX -->\n<section class=\"sec\" id=\"metbex\">\n  <div class=\"sec-top rv\">\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:14px\"><span class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"display:inline-flex;margin:0\">03 / M\u0259tb\u0259x</span> <span class=\"tag\">36 M\u0259hsul \u00b7 5 Alt Kateqoriya</span> <span class=\"eco\">HACCP</span></div>\n      <h2 class=\"h2\">M\u0259tb\u0259x <b>Gigiyena</b></h2>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"sec-desc\">Kommersiya m\u0259tb\u0259xi \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn x\u00fcsusi formulalar. F\u0131r\u0131n, degreaser, qabyuyan, food-grade sanitizer. HACCP uy\u011fun \u2014 no-rinse versiyalar m\u00f6vcuddur.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pg pg3 rv\">\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571902943202-507ec2618e8f?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"G\u00fccl\u00fc f\u0131r\u0131n v\u0259 gril t\u0259mizl\u0259yici \u2014 yanm\u0131\u015f ya\u011f \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-code\">MTB-001</div><div class=\"pc-name\">Oven / Grill Cleaner \u2014 Heavy-Duty</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Sodium hydroxide + solvents</li><li>Yanm\u0131\u015f ya\u011f &amp; karbon \u00e7\u0131xarma</li><li>Y\u00fcks\u0259k q\u0259l\u0259vi formula</li><li>\u018ftirsiz &amp; eco var</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 1 / 5 L</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556909114-f6e7ad7d3136?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Kommersiya m\u0259tb\u0259xi \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn ya\u011f \u00e7\u0131xar\u0131c\u0131 vasit\u0259\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-code\">MTB-002</div><div class=\"pc-name\">Kitchen Degreaser Konsentrat</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Alkalin + surfactant \u2014 dilutable</li><li>M\u0259tb\u0259x ya\u011flar\u0131 \u2014 intensiv t\u0259mizlik</li><li>1 / 5 / 10 / 20 L h\u0259cml\u0259r</li><li>\u018ftirsiz &amp; eco var</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 1 \u2013 20 L</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556742049-0cfed4f6a45d?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Cilalanm\u0131\u015f paslanmaz polad m\u0259tb\u0259x avadanl\u0131\u011f\u0131\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-code\">MTB-003</div><div class=\"pc-name\">Stainless Steel Cleaner</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Solvent + mineral oil</li><li>Anti-fingerprint \u2014 parlaql\u0131q</li><li>M\u0259tb\u0259x paslanmaz avadanl\u0131qlar\u0131</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 500 ml / 1 L</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585421514284-efb74c2b69ba?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"M\u0259tb\u0259x \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn maye qab yuma vasit\u0259si\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-code\">MTB-004</div><div class=\"pc-name\">Manual Dishwashing Liquid</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Surfactants + glycerin baza</li><li>K\u00f6p\u00fck n\u0259zar\u0259t formulas\u0131</li><li>\u018ftirsiz &amp; eco var</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 500 ml / 1 / 5 L</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556909212-d5b604d0c90d?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Qida s\u0259nayesi \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn sanitayzer sprey \u015f\u00fc\u015f\u0259si\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-code\">MTB-005</div><div class=\"pc-name\">Food-Grade Sanitizer RTU</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>QAC + water \u2014 no-rinse formula</li><li>HACCP + food-contact uy\u011fun</li><li>\u018ftirsiz &amp; eco var</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 500 ml / 1 L</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Restoran \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn kommersiya qabyuyan ma\u015f\u0131n\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-code\">MTB-006</div><div class=\"pc-name\">Avtomatik Qabyuyan Deterjan\u0131</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Alkalin builders + chelators</li><li>Auto dosing pump sistemi</li><li>Rinse aid ayr\u0131ca m\u00f6vcuddur</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 5 / 20 L</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- AMENITY -->\n<section id=\"amenity\" style=\"border-top:1px solid var(--border)\">\n  <div class=\"am-split\">\n    <div class=\"am-vis\">\n      <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1596178060671-7a80dc8059ea?w=900&q=80\" alt=\"L\u00fcks otel amenity tualetnik \u015f\u00fc\u015f\u0259l\u0259ri\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\">\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"am-body rv\">\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:18px\"><span class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"display:inline-flex;margin:0\">04 / Amenity</span> <span class=\"tag\">62 M\u0259hsul \u00b7 14 Alt Kateqoriya</span></div>\n      <h2 class=\"h2\" style=\"margin-bottom:20px\">Hotel <b>Amenity</b><br>X\u0259tti</h2>\n      <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.9;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:26px\">Standard v\u0259 Premium seriyalar. INCI sertifikat\u0131. Logo \u00e7apl\u0131 f\u0259rdi qabla\u015fd\u0131rma. 20 ml \u2013 300 ml formatlar. 5 ulduzlu standart \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn x\u00fcsusi haz\u0131rlanm\u0131\u015f.</p>\n      <div class=\"s-row\">\n        <div class=\"ser\"><div class=\"ser-lbl\">Standard Seriya</div><div class=\"ser-desc\">Surfactants + conditioners + standart \u0259tir. INCI list. Logo \u00e7ap se\u00e7imi m\u00f6vcuddur.</div></div>\n        <div class=\"ser prem\"><div class=\"ser-lbl\" style=\"color:var(--gold2)\">\u2726 Premium Seriya</div><div class=\"ser-desc\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,.55)\">Luxury fragrance blend. Embossed qabla\u015fd\u0131rma. Premium tekstura.</div></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pills\">\n        <div class=\"pill\"><div class=\"pn\">\u015eampun</div><div class=\"ps\">20/30/50/300 ml</div></div>\n        <div class=\"pill\"><div class=\"pn\">Du\u015f Geli</div><div class=\"ps\">20/30/50/300 ml</div></div>\n        <div class=\"pill\"><div class=\"pn\">Sabun Bar</div><div class=\"ps\">20/30/50/100 g</div></div>\n        <div class=\"pill\"><div class=\"pn\">Losyon</div><div class=\"ps\">20/30/50 ml</div></div>\n        <div class=\"pill\"><div class=\"pn\">Dental Kit</div><div class=\"ps\">F\u0131r\u00e7a + pasta</div></div>\n        <div class=\"pill\"><div class=\"pn\">Vanity Kit</div><div class=\"ps\">Pad + bud + file</div></div>\n        <div class=\"pill\"><div class=\"pn\">Terlikl\u0259r</div><div class=\"ps\">Logo tikm\u0259</div></div>\n        <div class=\"pill\"><div class=\"pn\">Du\u015f Papa\u011f\u0131</div><div class=\"ps\">PE plastic</div></div>\n        <div class=\"pill\"><div class=\"pn\">\u00dclg\u00fcc</div><div class=\"ps\">Twin blade</div></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- \u0130STEHLAK -->\n"}}}